title: Let the Aavegotchi DAO create a new mission
body:
We've got a strong, active community ready to be a DAO, and it would be interesting if we can test ourselves by creating our own mission! Complete with a proposal, voting, and discussion before it becomes an actual mission!

Of course, mission has got to be reasonable. Something easily doable like the other missions, and something that lets people learn more about Aavegotchi!
author: 0xBd810C549c287C759Ff9044EFeB1712bc1a58eDD
